title: Number of all operations in an slapd instance
agents: linux
catalog: app/slapd
license: GPL
distribution: Markus Weber
description:
 This check monitors all Operation types, you can set warn and crit
 thresholds to each type. There is also an deviance check wich alarms you about
 the ratio of Initiated to Completed operations

item:
 SLAPD <Instance name> Operations

[parameters]
parameters (dict):

perfdata:
 one for each operation type.

inventory:
 One service will be created for each slapd instance configured in lokal config file.
